						<summary>

						<p>On a stone in Survey No. 959.</p>						

						<p>Kumāra Hariyaṇṇa Oḍeya, A.D. 1380.</p>						

						<p>Dated Śaka 1302, <hi rend="italic">Raudri, Māgha</hi> śu. 1, Friday, corresponding to A.D. 1380, December 28.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Registers a gift of land to Basavaṁṇa, son of Dēvaṁṇa of Gautama-<hi rend="italic">gotra</hi> and Ṛik-<hi rend="italic">śākhā</hi> by the Chief.</p>						

